  <brief_title>The Effect of Oxytocin on the Acquisition and Consolidation of Trauma-Associated Memories</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Oxytocin on the Acquisition and Consolidation of Trauma-Associated Memories: A Model to Understand the Development of Posttraumatic Stress Disorder</official_title>
  <sponsors>
