  <source>Charite University, Berlin, Germany</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to examine whether oxytocin and oxytocin receptor gene
      polymorphism affect the development of intrusive memories, a cardinal symptom of PTSD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
